    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Sasanidus, a new generic name for Noemacheilus kermanshahensis Bănărescu & Nalbant, with discussion of Ilamnemacheilus and Schistura (Teleostei; Nemacheilidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271352>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271351>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271354>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271356>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271357> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271352>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Sasanidus kermanshahensis, about 45 mm SL, not preserved; Iran: Haram-Abad stream." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271351>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Maximum Likelihood estimation of the relationships based on the mitochondrial COI barcode region (Tamura 3 - parameter model, discrete Gamma distribution for rate differences with 5 categories + G parameter = 0.4706 and invariable site proportion + I = 58.22 %). Nucleotide positions with less than 100 % site coverage were eliminated resulting in 562 analysed positions. The tree is drawn to scale, with branch lengths measured in number of substitutions per site. Numbers of nodes indicate bootstrap values from 1000 pseudoreplicates and low values have deliberately been included to demonstrate the lack of evolutionary signal to resolve the relationships between supra-specific taxa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271351/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271354>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Sasanidus kermanshahensis, FSJF 3213, 63 mm SL; Iran: Gamasiab River." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271354/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271356>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Schistura rupecula, SMF 8993, syntype, 71 mm SL; India: Shimla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271357>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Schistura spp.: India: Karnataka: a, FSJF 3515, 50 mm SL; stream between Mukkodlu to Surlabhi; b, FSJF 3516, 36 mm SL; stream in Bhagamandala fields; c, FSJF 3517, 30 mm SL; rafting place at Barapol River; d, FSJF 3518, 52 mm SL; River above Kumadhara waterfalls." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

